data.description: Nicely remodeled one story home with two spacious living areas, large dining room in the heart of the home.  Kitchen offer granite countertops and custom cabinets with stainless appliances.  Second living room is spacious with wood burning fireplace and lots of natural light.  All windows were replaced recently along with roof, HVAC and water heater.  Lots to love about this well cared for home.
